        <type>void</type>
        <definition>void XVWarpFilter_IntrHandler</definition>
        <argsstring>(void *InstancePtr)</argsstring>
        <name>XVWarpFilter_IntrHandler</name>
        <param>
          <type>void *</type>
          <declname>InstancePtr</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Interrupt handler for the Warp Filter core. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This handler clears the pending interrupt and determines if the source is the frame done signal. If yes, it calls the registered callback function. The application is responsible for connecting this function to the interrupt system.</para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>InstancePtr</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is a pointer to the <ref refid="struct_x_v__warp__filter" kindref="compound">XV_warp_filter</ref> instance that just interrupted.</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>None.</para></simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>The application is responsible for connecting this function to the interrupt system. </para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
